* QED DEFINITIONS

version  SETSTR   1.01

* Macro for calling ERRMSG

ERRMSG   MACRO    A
[.LAB]   LEA      .S.[.L],A1
         BSR.[.EXT] ERRMSG
         SECTION  MSG
.S.[.L]  STRING$  {[A]}
         SECTION  CODE
         ENDM

* Equates

LF       EQU      $0A
K_TAB    EQU      9
K_ENTER  EQU      $0A
K_ESC    EQU      $1B
K_LEFT   EQU      $C0
K_RIGHT  EQU      $C8
K_UP     EQU      $D0
K_DOWN   EQU      $D8
K.ALT    EQU      $01      MASK FOR ALT
K.CTRL   EQU      $02      MASK FOR CTRL
K.SHIFT  EQU      $04      MASK FOR SHIFT
K_F1     EQU      $E8
K_F2     EQU      $EC
K_F3     EQU      $F0
K_SHF3   EQU      $F2
K_F4     EQU      $F4
K_F5     EQU      $F8

* Storage definitions

         OFFSET   0

